1. *Mesecima* nisam čula ništa o njemu. (I haven't heard anything about him for months.)
2. Prošlo je *mesecima* od kada smo se poslednji put videli. (It's been months since we last saw each other.)
3. Oni su putovali *mesecima* pre nego što su stigli do cilja. (They traveled for months before reaching their destination.)
4. Ovaj projekat traje *mesecima* i konačno se bliži kraju. (This project has been going on for months and is finally nearing completion.)
5. Sve *mesecima* radimo na ovome, i sada smo konačno videli rezultate. (We've been working on this for months, and now we finally see the results.)
6. Ona je *mesecima* planirala svoje venčanje. (She planned her wedding for months.)
7. *Mesecima* unazad, imamo problema sa internet konekcijom. (For months now, we've been having internet connection issues.)
8. Moram da štedim novac *mesecima* kako bih mogao da putujem. (I have to save money for months to be able to travel.)
9. *Mesecima* sam se trudila da naučim novi jezik. (I've been trying to learn a new language for months.)
10. Ovo je već *mesecima* najveći izazov sa kojim se suočavamo. (This has been the biggest challenge we've faced for months.)

(Note: In Serbian, "mesecima" means "for months" or "months ago," depending on the context.)